Class DescriptorModelProvider

    GeneratorDescriptorModelProvider, GenericDescriptorModelProvider, LanguageDescriptorModelProvider
    public abstract class DescriptorModelProvider

    Common code for all contributors of descriptor models. Methods with SModule are invoked from respective methods of repository listener, model access is identical to that of original notification.
